{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "反藝術運動", "storyInfo": "ELA希望確認雷內爾的清白，可雷內爾懶得自辯。受到重大打擊的社區居民們聞訊更加憤怒，加上上尉臥底的煽風點火，人們決定朝藝術館進發。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA小姐……你怎麼來了？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#4$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾在哪裡？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在陽台上打高爾夫……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，ELA小姐！", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#4$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g10_deluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_whshglf"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉……剛剛那顆球打到你了？你這麼生氣做什麼？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#7$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就在昨天，迪亞茲的社區出事了。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出事？什麼事？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#6$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們的藝術節表演被毀了個徹底，你不知道嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你這是什麼興師問罪的語氣？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#11$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什曾經找到我說，希望我能說服社區裡的人推遲他們的藝術節表演，不要和你的開幕式撞了時間。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，是我讓米沃什去找你談的。所以你認為……因為你沒答應，我便授意別人去做了這事。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在你身邊擔任保鏢時，我有很多次見到米沃什去找那位上尉談合作，他運送藥物的倉庫又在你名下。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在看來，你們的關係並沒有表現出來的那麼緊張，他甚至在你開幕式的邀請名單上。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有很多疑點我在當時沒有細究，但如今出事了，我得來問問你。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，ELA小姐，妳是心裡帶著答案來問我的嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有預設答案，我想聽你的解釋。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……我主動找上他並不是為了跟他合作，只是……想看他笑話。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼多人都在那片社區吃過虧，我想，說不定那傢伙也能在他們手下吃點苦頭。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實的確如此，不管你信不信，我沒有指使他去做這件事……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許你的本意並非如此……但你有想過這樣做可能帶來的後果嗎，雷內爾？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓一位武裝部隊的首領直接對上了一群手無寸鐵的社區平民。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有想到結果會……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者你根本不在乎！", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#4$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了安放你龐大的自我，你建造了這座華美的藝術館。這難道不夠嗎？為什麼你還要一次次地招惹那些與你毫無關係的人？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？你需要靠這些來證明你的存在感嗎，雷內爾？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，ELA小姐，你該離開了。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，我一直很想問，你在這樣一個龐然大物身邊，有足夠的空間喘息嗎？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……出去。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，ELA小姐，如果你執意要為這齣慘劇找個罪魁禍首，那你就當是我做的吧。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你該離開了，ELA。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_whshglf"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i02", "fadetime": 0.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人背過身站定，不再理會ELA，隨即重心輕移，肩膀內旋，優雅俐落地揮出一桿。"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "球在空中劃出一道曲線，本應落在距離洞口一米開外，可高爾夫球詭異地改變了原先的路線，滑進了球洞。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA從球筐裡隨手拾起一顆球，舉高在陽光下。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我就注意到了，無論你打出的球拋物線有多麼刁鑽古怪，最終都會落進洞裡。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生，身為雷內爾最親近的人，你能告訴我為什麼嗎？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米沃什"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你這輩子有沒有試過靠自己的本事揮出一桿，雷內爾？在空中揮出一道真實的曲線。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘗試過很多次。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果如何？", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "心力交瘁，那片草地根本沒有球洞，我只是徒勞。", "name": "雷內爾"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那真是太遺憾了。", "name": "ELA"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘆了口氣，ELA將手中的高爾夫球擲出，在草坪上滾過幾圈後，那顆球緩緩滾進球洞。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何，事情辦妥了嗎？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，連撤退的時機都掌握得很精準，來多索雷斯這麼久，我第一次覺得你們把事情辦得很漂亮。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那四個人？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心，那個小個子不是被你們傷得很重嗎？", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個社區現在估計都熱血上頭，他們攔不住的。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕快回來，還有更大的事情要做。這件事辦妥了，你們和我就都穩當了。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼一半人不一半人的，我們這次是全數押上，興廢在此一舉，都給我提起精神點。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，所有人都撤回到藝術館，部署好後隨時待命。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越多越好，成本和我們的收益相比根本不值一提。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#7$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，還有，最後一件事。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得往社區裡塞幾個腦子精明、嘴巴靈活、跑得也快的傢伙，把社區煽動起來，免得他們真的按兵不動。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g3_galleriessquare_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……但願一天時間足夠那幫不成器的傢伙把社區煽動起來。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上尉長舒了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管藝術館外已經為開幕式佈置好了座位和舞台，到場的人還不算太多。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？真無聊，我還以為早點到會有什麼暖場活動呢！", "name": "早到的遊客"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有好幾個小時，你看看來了幾個人？就你在那邊急。", "name": "不情願的遊客"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈……", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你笑什麼？", "name": "早到的遊客"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來得早說不定會有驚喜呢。", "name": "馬特奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1210_1#9$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們下手太重，我現在只能做到這一步，你的右手……以後可能很難再做一些精細動作了。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精細動作？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如寫字，畫畫……我很抱歉。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……又不是你的錯。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記得明天來換藥。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#2$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……要是我能早一分鐘下樓……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也別太自責，這裡的人不論是速度還是身體素質都比我們強太多，我們很難追趕……", "name": "FUZE"}, "figure_art": "avg_4126_fuze_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，可就在我面前，那個軍官——", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#2$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA，你回來了。雷內爾怎麼說？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事並非他指使，但如今的局面也與他脫不了關係。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這又是什麼話？你是在為他開脫嗎，ELA？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……雷內爾曾經聯繫過那位上尉，示意他只要能解決社區裡的“麻煩傢伙”，這片地皮的開發權就歸他所有。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道這還不算是指使嗎？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他告訴我，他的本意只是想讓那個得罪他的上尉在社區這裡吃點苦頭……他知道社區裡的人不好惹。", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他要不要親自來看看這裡變成了什麼樣子？這種話他居然也說得出口？！", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#3$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冷靜，卡提布。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#10$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算我能冷靜，那社區裡的大家呢？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看外面那些人，他們要如何在聽到雷內爾那番言論後冷靜下來？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "48_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 35.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走在人群中央，四個人感受到了濃濃的絕望。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們頹喪地坐在道路兩旁，置身於一片狼藉之中，彷彿被抽走了靈魂。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡曾經寄託著他們的熱情，努力，靈感。但現在，什麼都沒剩下。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "環顧四周，有些人緩緩抬起頭，空洞地注視著彼此的面容。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但更多人只是坐在原地，不知自己究竟還能做些什麼。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ELA，ELA！", "name": "特克諾"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾？", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是雷內爾，是不是那個傢伙為了自己的開幕式，讓那些聯合政府的混帳毀掉了我們的心血？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特克諾……有些事情我們還需要確認，但我不認為……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#7$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不認為什麼？！你以前是雷內爾的保鏢，自然是幫著他說話！", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，我們就該來個以牙還牙！", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在就去他的藝術館……", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓大家帶著那些殘骸，到了後直接砸到雷內爾那混蛋的藝術館上——", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#7$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不覺得這樣太軟弱了嗎？", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軟弱？那你還想怎麼辦？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許我們可以衝進美術館，讓雷內爾和他的小秘書付出血的代價。", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）人群裡有人在煽動，有人想激化事態。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸位，還請冷靜……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是……我們恐怕打不過他們……我腰肌勞損很多年，做不了這種打打殺殺的事情。", "name": "孱弱多病的畫家"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也是，我有腰椎間盤突出……", "name": "身體虛弱的琴師"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我唯一能夠傷害別人的利器就是我的真誠，我的肉體不堪一擊……", "name": "非常瘦弱的歌手"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……我倒是練過幾年，但是我暈血啊……", "name": "體格強健的雕塑家"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）或許事態也沒有激化到那個地步……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的骨氣呢？就這麼打碎牙齒和血吞嗎？", "name": "古怪的社區居民"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，好不甘心……毀掉我們的藝術節後，憑什麼他的開幕式就能順利進行下去。", "name": "身體虛弱的琴師"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹……你怎麼想？", "name": "非常瘦弱的歌手"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，抄傢伙，我們去那個玻璃房子。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不會真的要去打架吧？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#6$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪亞茲先生，等等……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#5$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我是讓你們帶上音響和樂器……既然我們的場地沒有了，那就去雷內爾的藝術館門口跳。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些人越不想看我們的舞姿，我們就越要讓他們看見。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轟的一聲，人群突然躁動起來，彷彿點燃的火柴掉進了乾燥的柴草堆。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）那現在怎麼辦……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#7$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……先跟著一起去吧……", "name": "ELA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4123_ela_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）這……我們的目標算是達到了嗎？", "name": "古怪的社區居民"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我也不知道，但是無論如何，他們確實是要去藝術館了……", "name": "陌生的社區居民"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）報告，鼷獸已經探頭出洞。", "name": "古怪的社區居民"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g5_galleries", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，請問這件花瓶要放在哪裡？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，在第三展廳。", "name": "藝術館安保人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_020"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你走錯方向了，先生，第三展廳在那邊。", "name": "藝術館安保人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，不好意思，我是新來的。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（整個藝術館都找遍了，除了這個地方，嚴防死守，想了各種辦法都很難混進去。）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（可惡，明明所有線索都指向了這裡……）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（有人來了……）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_020", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等開幕式就要開始了，米沃什先生要求館內人員全部離開，參加廣場上的開幕式。", "name": "藝術館工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_020", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也要去嗎？", "name": "藝術館安保人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_223", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米沃什先生特別強調了，所有人，一個也不能留在這裡。", "name": "藝術館工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_223"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_020", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好……兄弟們，我們走吧。", "name": "藝術館安保人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_020"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪，一場發表會竟然需要所有人去看……雷內爾這是什麼意思？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和其他的地方相比，這裡也沒什麼特別的啊。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從口袋中掏出一把玻璃球，埃內斯托將它們輕輕放在地上，本應在水平地面上靜止不動的圓球竟然全部滾向了一個地方。"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地面有輕微的傾斜情況……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（敲擊牆壁）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然不出所料，有道暗門在這裡。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜……大概是這幅平平無奇的畫？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有兩個小時發布會就要開始了，已經有提早到場的人開始落座了。你決定開幕典禮上要講什麼了嗎？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不重要，反正只是為了拖時間，從那些遞上來的方案裡面隨便選一樣就好了，我看那個什麼虛擬藝術藏品就不錯。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "示範時的背景圖片用哪張？藝術館裡的畫？", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就用馬特奧的照片。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣羞辱他，依他的性格可能會當場暴怒。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擔心什麼，我邀請他不就是為了羞辱他嗎？況且到了這個時候，你覺得我還會在乎他的小脾氣嗎？", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起底下人目睹藝術館爆炸後的絕望心情，他的憤怒的確不值一提。", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#1$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些投資在這裡的錢財，從藝術品市場掘金的宏圖，都會隨著這場爆炸付之一炬。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些被炒出天價卻其實一文不值的垃圾，那些被扭曲了表達與訴說的畸形造物……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些無人問津，一直被丟在倉庫，只有轉手倒賣時才會被拿出的真正藝術……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看那些唯利是圖的人對它們做了什麼？現在好了，它們都能在火焰中找到歸處。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來幾年，恐怕整個藝術品市場都要陷入混亂了……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#2$1"}, {"id": 460, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是我要的……每當那些投資商回憶起這天，他們便會膽寒，便會害怕……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們會看見藝術品真正的價值，再也不敢將藝術品貶為一件貨物。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那些為此而痛苦的藝術家，他們也能從這個畸形的市場中解脫出來。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#8$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#7$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真可惜啊，媽媽和老東西都不在……", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 469, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1213_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷內爾……", "name": "米沃什"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1213_1#5$1"}, {"id": 471, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陪我坐一下吧，米沃什。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#10$1"}, {"id": 473, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陪我等待第二天的到來。", "name": "雷內爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1211_1#2$1"}, {"id": 475, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 479, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好黑啊，一點光都沒有……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好帶了手電筒。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 490, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嚥口水）", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 492, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這是……？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 493, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順著手電筒發出的光線，埃內斯托看見暗室的地板上堆滿了包裝袋，裡面的易燃物被整齊地堆放在靠牆的位置。"}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "層層疊疊，一直堆到天花板。"}}, {"id": 497, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 498, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 499, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 500, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 501, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 502, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 503, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}